INSERT INTO `produit` VALUES (2,'Nike Blazar Mid\'77','air-force-1',600,500,'1717257486611.jpg','Nike Blazer Casablanca Maroc','[\"1717257486618.jpg\",\"1717257486629.jpg\",\"1717257486631.jpg\"]','[\"1717257486618.jpg\",\"1717257486629.jpg\",\"1717257486631.jpg\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\",\"42\",\"43\" ]','Imaginée dans les années 70. Adoptée dans les années 80. Sanctifiée dans les années 90. Prête pour la suite. La Nike Blazer Mid ’77 présente un design intemporel et facile à porter. Confortable et incroyablement soignée, son empeigne en cuir brillant s’associe à un logo rétro audacieux et à des détails en daim luxueux pour un confort exceptionnel. La mousse visible sur la languette et la finition spéciale sur la semelle intermédiaire donnent l\'impression que tu as conservé cette paire depuis des décennies. N\'attends plus et entre dans l\'histoire.',0,1,'[\"2\", \"2\", \"4\", \"5\"]','homme','new','nike-blazar-mid77'),(3,'Nike Dunk Low','dunk',400,350,'1717527214976.png','mike dunk casablanca maroc','[\"1717527214985.png\",\"1717527214988.png\",\"1717527215008.png\"]','[\"1717527214985.png\",\"1717527214988.png\",\"1717527215008.png\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\",\"42\",\"43\" ]','The Nike Dunk Low is an easy score for your closet. This mid-‘80s hoops icon returns with super-durable construction and original colors. With ankle padding and rubber traction, this one is a slam dunk.',0,1,'[\"1\", \"3\", \"3\", \"5\"]','homme','new','nike-dunk-low'),(4,'Nike Air Max 2017','air-force-1',800,750,'1717527834612.png','Nike Air Max 2017 casablanca maroc','[\"1717527834639.jpeg\",\"1717527834645.png\",\"1717527834649.png\"]','[\"1717527834639.jpeg\",\"1717527834645.png\",\"1717527834649.png\"]','[ \"41\",\"42\",\"43\" ]','The Nike Air Max 2017 delivers the plush sensation you love with a full-length Max Air unit. The upper is seamlessly constructed with zonal support and ventilation while molded foam wraps your mid-foot and heel for secure comfort.',0,1,'[\"1\", \"3\", \"4\"]','homme','new','nike-air-max-2017'),(7,'Air Jordan 6 Retro \"White/Black\"','air-jordan',2000,1900,'1718218956151.png','air jordan nike casablanca','[\"1718218956157.png\",\"1718218956163.png\",\"1718218956169.png\"]','[\"1718218956157.png\",\"1718218956163.png\",\"1718218956169.png\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\",\"42\" ]','MJ wore \'em when he claimed his first championship and you\'ll be wearing \'em for—well, whatever you want. Laden with dynamic design lines and those iconic lace locks, these sneakers bring throwback style to any \'fit. Lace up, and let your kicks do the talking.',0,1,'[0, \"3\", \"4\"]','homme','new','air-jordan-6-retro-whiteblack'),(8,'Jordan Spizike Low','air-jordan',1600,0,'1718219835664.png','Jordane Spizike Casablanca','[\"1718219835673.png\",\"1718219835681.png\",\"1718219835682.png\"]','[\"1718219835673.png\",\"1718219835681.png\",\"1718219835682.png\"]','[ \"41\",\"42\",\"43\" ]','The Spizike takes elements of five classic Jordans, combines them, and gives you one iconic sneaker. It\'s an homage to Spike Lee formally introducing Hollywood and hoops in a culture moment. You get a great looking pair of kicks with some history.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\",\"4\" ]','homme','latest-arrival','jordan-spizike-low'),(9,'Air Jordan 1 Low OG \"Black/Gorge Green\"','air-jordan',400,0,'1718220532372.jpg','air jordan casablanca','[\"1718220532394.png\",\"1718220532424.png\",\"1718220532430.jpg\"]','[\"1718220532394.png\",\"1718220532424.png\",\"1718220532430.jpg\"]','[ \"38\",\"39\" ]','Step into greatness with the Air Jordan 1 Low OG. Updated color and texture gives the all-time favorite fresh identity while staying true to the original design.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\"]','homme','latest-arrival','air-jordan-1-low-og-blackgorge-green'),(10,'Nike Dunk Low Retro SE','dunk',400,0,'1718543835676.png','Nike Dunk Low Retro SE Casablanca','[\"1718543835684.png\",\"1718543835694.png\",\"1718543835697.png\"]','[\"1718543835684.png\",\"1718543835694.png\",\"1718543835697.png\"]','[ \"39\",\"40\",\"41\",\"42\" ]','L\'icône du basket des années 80 revient avec des couleurs cultes, du cuir impeccable et un style basket rétro. Le style vintage fait son retour dans ton quotidien. Et son col rembourré te permet de la porter partout dans un confort total.',0,1,'[\"1\", \"3\", \"4\", \"5\"]','homme','latest-arrival','nike-dunk-low-retro-se'),(11,'Air Jordan 1 Retro High','air-jordan',600,0,'1718548381103.jpeg','Air Jordan 1 Retro High Casablanca','[\"1718548381117.jpeg\",\"1718548381126.jpeg\",\"1718548381150.jpeg\"]','[\"1718548381117.jpeg\",\"1718548381126.jpeg\",\"1718548381150.jpeg\"]','[ \"41\",\"42\",\"43\" ]','Chaque Jordan Retro est un modèle culte revisité avec de nouvelles couleurs et textures. Cette version s\'inspire de ton jean fétiche pour un style denim épuré. Matières et détails premium dans l\'air du temps.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\",\"4\" ]','homme','latest-arrival','air-jordan-1-retro-high'),(12,'Air Jordan 1 Mid','air-jordan',700,0,'1718549070408.jpeg','Air Jordan 1 Mid Casablanca','[\"1718549070425.png\",\"1718549070427.png\",\"1718549070435.jpeg\"]','[\"1718549070425.png\",\"1718549070427.png\",\"1718549070435.jpeg\"]','[ \"40\",\"40.5\",\"41\",\"42\",\"42.5\",\"43\" ]','Inspiré de la AJ1 originale, ce modèle mi-montant conserve le look emblématique que vous aimez tant, tandis que le choix des couleurs et le cuir impeccable lui confèrent une identité unique.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\",\"4\",\"5\",\"6\",\"7\"]','homme','release','air-jordan-1-mid'),(13,'Jumpman MVP','air-jordan',400,0,'1718549356462.png','Jumpman MVP Casablanca','[\"1718549356468.png\",\"1718549356470.png\",\"1718549356480.jpeg\"]','[\"1718549356468.png\",\"1718549356470.png\",\"1718549356480.jpeg\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\",\"42\" ]','Pour cette version remixée, on a eu l\'embarras du choix. On a repris des éléments des AJ6, 7 et 8 pour créer une toute nouvelle chaussure qui rend hommage aux trois titres consécutifs de Michael Jordan. Avec leurs détails en cuir, tissu et nubuck, ces sneakers rendent hommage à un héritage et t\'invitent à tracer ta propre légende.',0,1,'[1, \"3\", \"4\"]','homme','release','jumpman-mvp'),(14,'dsjs','air-jordan',750,540,'1719504286901.jpg','shsjdmkn','[\"1719504286924.png\",\"1719504286973.png\",\"1719504286981.jpg\"]','[\"1719504286924.png\",\"1719504286973.png\",\"1719504286981.jpg\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\" ]','asxsklmsd sxlxsmkxs skxsplplxsk xslxospdppxs sxlslskxjjhxsjh',0,1,'[\"0\", \"0\"]','homme','release','dsjs'),(27,'Air Jordan 1 Low SE','air-jordan',900,0,'1719859384501.jpeg','Air Jordan 1 Low SE Casablanca','[\"1719859384520.jpeg\",\"1719859384643.png\",\"1719859384738.png\"]','[\"1719859384520.jpeg\",\"1719859384643.png\",\"1719859384738.png\"]','[ \"39\",\"40\",\"43\" ]','Fresh colors and textures give you an updated AJ1 without losing its iconic silhouette and familiar feel. Made from premium materials, this all-time favorite comes decked out with comfortable Nike Air cushioning and subtle design details (check out that embroidered heel) to give you a staple sneaker with a modern look.\r\n\r\n',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\",\"4\" ]','homme','release','air-jordan-1-low-se'),(28,'Nike Air Force 1 Flyknit 2.0','air-force-1',1200,1000,'1722004819088.png','air-force-flykint casablanca','[\"1722004819117.jpeg\",\"1722004819134.jpeg\",\"1722004819143.png\"]','[\"1722004819117.jpeg\",\"1722004819134.jpeg\",\"1722004819143.png\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\" ]','Inspirée par la chaussure qui règne sur les terrains depuis 1982, la Nike Air Force 1 Flyknit 2.0 fait revivre la AF1 dans un modèle encore plus léger que jamais. Arborant la conception Flyknit avec les lignes AF1 classiques, elle rappelle le style basketball old school dans une version offrant davantage de légèreté.\r\n\r\n',0,1,'[1, \"3\"]','homme','new','nike-air-force-1-flyknit-20'),(29,'Nike - Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Shield - Black White',NULL,1700,0,'1722945445360.jpg','Nike - Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Shield - Black White','[\"1722945445365.jpg\",\"1722945445366.jpeg\",\"1722945445371.png\"]','[\"1722945445365.jpg\",\"1722945445366.jpeg\",\"1722945445371.png\"]','[ \"40\",\"39\" ]','Conquer the elements and power through your runs with the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Shield. Designed to provide optimal performance and protection in challenging weather conditions, these running shoes are equipped with innovative features to keep you comfortable and focused on your goals. Whether it\'s rain, wind, or cold, the Pegasus 38 Shield has got you covered.\r\n\r\nFeaturing a water-repellent upper, these shoes keep your feet dry and shielded from the elements. The durable and weather-resistant materials ensure long-lasting wear, allowing you to confidently tackle wet terrains and unpredictable weather. Rain or shine, you can count on the Pegasus 38 Shield to deliver exceptional performance.\r\n\r\nThe Air Zoom cushioning technology provides a responsive and cushioned ride, absorbing impact and delivering energy return with every stride. This lightweight and springy foam not only enhances your comfort but also propels you forward, helping you achieve your best running performance.\r\n\r\nWith a secure and adaptive fit, the Pegasus 38 Shield keeps your feet supported and stable throughout your run. The updated FlyEase lacing system allows for easy on and off, while the lockdown fit ensures a snug and personalized feel. The padded collar and tongue provide added comfort, reducing friction and irritation for a distraction-free running experience.\r\n\r\nEquipped with a durable rubber outsole, these shoes offer excellent traction on wet surfaces, keeping you stable and confident even in slippery conditions. The multidirectional grooves provide enhanced grip, allowing you to maintain control and agility on various terrains.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re training for a race or simply enjoying your daily run, the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 38 Shield is your reliable companion. Its combination of performance-driven features, weather protection, and comfortable design makes it the perfect choice for runners seeking to conquer any weather conditions.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"4\" ]','homme, femme','new','nike---air-zoom-pegasus-38-shield---black-white'),(30,'Air-Jordan-1-Mid SE-Craft','Air-Jordan-1, Air-Force-1',900,0,'1723136411648.jpg','Air-Jordan-1-Mid SE-Craft Casablanca','[\"1723136411660.jpeg\",\"1723136411691.jpg\",\"1723136411734.jpeg\"]','[\"1723136411660.jpeg\",\"1723136411691.jpg\",\"1723136411734.jpeg\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\" ]','The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Craft redefines the classic AJ1 with a blend of premium materials and a unique color palette. This special edition features an anthracite and olive combination, utilizing both suede and leather to create a sophisticated look. The mid-top silhouette provides excellent ankle support, while the Air-Sole unit offers responsive cushioning for maximum comfort. The shoe\'s construction ensures durability, making it a versatile option for both casual wear and more formal occasions. Iconic branding elements, such as the Jumpman logo and Wings logo, add to its appeal.',0,1,'[ \"2\",\"3\" ]','femme, homme','new','air-jordan-1-mid-se-craft'),(31,'Air-Jordan-1-Mid SE-Craft','Air-Force-1, Air-Jordan-1',900,0,'1723138632743.jpg','Air-Jordan-1-Mid SE-Craft Casablanca','[\"1723138632751.jpeg\",\"1723138632783.jpg\",\"1723138632795.jpeg\"]','[\"1723138632751.jpeg\",\"1723138632783.jpg\",\"1723138632795.jpeg\"]','[ \"40\",\"41\" ]','The Air Jordan 1 Mid SE Craft redefines the classic AJ1 with a blend of premium materials and a unique color palette. This special edition features an anthracite and olive combination, utilizing both suede and leather to create a sophisticated look. The mid-top silhouette provides excellent ankle support, while the Air-Sole unit offers responsive cushioning for maximum comfort. The shoe\'s construction ensures durability, making it a versatile option for both casual wear and more formal occasions. Iconic branding elements, such as the Jumpman logo and Wings logo, add to its appeal.',0,1,'[ \"2